<head>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho Pro', serif;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
      color: #000;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(173, 216, 230, 0.7), rgba(144, 238, 144, 0.7)), url('428625.jpg');
      background-position: left center; 
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      padding-top: 60px;  /* Adjust this according to your header height */
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #007f5f;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #00593f;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .board-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #007f5f;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .board-link:hover {
      background-color: #00593f;
    }

    .catchphrase {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .spacer {
      height: 50px; /* 適切な高さに調整してください */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <%= link_to "問診を始める", new_symptom_path, class: 'cta-button' %>
  <p class="catchphrase">身体の痛みをケアしましょう</p>
  <div class="intro">
    <p>自宅でできるセルフケア方法を学びましょう</p>
  </div>
  <div class="spacer"></div> <!-- 新しく追加 -->
  <a href="#" class="board-link">掲示板</a>
  <p class="catchphrase">痛みの共有掲示板で支え合いの輪を広げよう</p>
</div>

</body>
